dict.string: Pets Home needs your consent to access the camera to shoot personal works/personal portraits. If prohibited, you will not be able to take photos or update information.
Pets Home requires your consent to obtain location information when using it in order to upload photos or update avatars. If prohibited, you will not be able to publish works/update avatars.
Pets Home requires your consent to obtain location information when using it in order to upload photos or update avatars. If prohibited, you will not be able to publish works/update avatars.
Pets Home requires your consent to obtain location information when using it in order to upload photos or update avatars. If prohibited, you will not be able to publish works/update avatars.
Pets Home needs your permission to access the microphone. If blocked, you will not be able to send audio messages to users.

Pets needs your consent to access the album to select photos to upload/publish works/update avatars. If prohibited, you will not be able to upload selected photos to upload/publish works/update avatars.
Pets occasionally uses identifiers to push personalized ads
